  <compounddef id="CSD" kind="page">
    <compoundname>CSD</compoundname>
    <title>CSD$ Function</title>
    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">CSD$</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>Returns the <bold>current working directory</bold> for the process as a string. The result is always an <bold>absolute path</bold> from the virtual file system root (<computeroutput>/</computeroutput>).</para>
<para>Newly spawned processes inherit the current directory of their parent process.</para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<sect1 id="CSD_1examples-91_1s1"><sect2 id="CSD_1examples-91_1s2"><sect3 id="CSD_1examples-91">
<title>Examples</title><para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">PRINT<sp/>CSD$</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>Might produce:</para>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">/home/user/projects</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">REM<sp/>Save<sp/>current<sp/>directory,<sp/>change,<sp/>then<sp/>restore</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">oldDir$<sp/>=<sp/>CSD$</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">CHDIR<sp/>&quot;/tmp&quot;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">PRINT<sp/>&quot;Now<sp/>in<sp/>&quot;;<sp/>CSD$</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">CHDIR<sp/>oldDir$</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">PRINT<sp/>&quot;Back<sp/>in<sp/>&quot;;<sp/>CSD$</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
</sect3></sect2></sect1>
<sect1 id="CSD_1notes-90_1s1"><sect2 id="CSD_1notes-90_1s2"><sect3 id="CSD_1notes-90">
<title>Notes</title><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>The returned path always begins with <computeroutput>/</computeroutput>.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>A process’ working directory may be changed with <ref refid="CHDIR" kindref="compound">CHDIR</ref>.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Child processes inherit the parent’s working directory at the moment they are spawned.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
